dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Jeremy Butler. May I have your name, please?
Hello, Jeremy. My name is Samantha Hayes.
Nice to meet you, Samantha. Could you please provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is five five two four one and my date of birth is zero six one three nineteen ninety.
Thank you, Samantha. One last thing, could you please confirm the make and model of your car and the names of any additional drivers on your policy?
The make and model of my car is Toyota Camry, and the additional driver on my policy is my husband, James Hayes.
Thank you for providing the information, Samantha. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, Jeremy. That's all for now. Thank you for your help.
You're welcome, Samantha. If you have any more questions in the future, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
